
<p class="lead home_para"><strong>The African Poetry Digital Portal</strong> is a project of the <a href="about_africanpoetrybookfund">African Poetry Book Fund</a>. The Portal  is a resource for the study of the history of African Poetry providing access to biographical information, artifacts, news, video recording, images and documents related to African poetry from antiquity to the present. It will also feature specially curated digital projects on various aspects of African poetry. </p>

